  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Scottish Labour Market Statistics for three months to August 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Unemployment in Scotland rose by 12,000 over the last 12 months.</p>

  </div>
</div>

